Name: iw.debug
Version: 0.3
Summary: Tools to help debugging a zope based application
Home-page: https://ingeniweb.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/ingeniweb/iw.debug
Author: Ingeniweb
Author-email: support@ingeniweb.com
